posts.name: Jackson
posts.cooked: Here is my code for driveRobotRelative(ChassisSpeeds speeds), which is required to run pathplanner. public void driveRobotRelative(ChassisSpeeds speeds) { System.out.println(speeds.vxMetersPerSecond); System.out.println(speeds.vyMetersPerSecond); System.out.println(speeds.omegaRadiansPerSecond); speedsC.withSpeeds(speeds); applyRequest(() → speedsC); } The robot is able to drive normally with swerve.  When I run autonomous, it prints out a bunch of numbers, but never sets the speed of the chassis.  Does anyone know why?
